{
  "uid": "v12-4-profiles-dd",
  "title": "Grafana 12.4 — Profiles Drilldown + Flame Graph",
  "description": "Profiles Drilldown (on top of Pyroscope) went GA in 12.0 and 12.4 added the Profiles Assistant. This dashboard wires a flame-graph panel against the Pyroscope datasource + surfaces Pyroscope's self-profile so you have something to look at.",
  "tags": ["grafana-12", "v12.0", "v12.4", "profiles", "pyroscope", "flamegraph", "v12-demo"],
  "schemaVersion": 40,
  "version": 1,
  "editable": true,
  "refresh": "30s",
  "time": {"from": "now-15m", "to": "now"},
  "timepicker": {},
  "templating": {"list": [
    {"name": "ds_pyro", "type": "datasource", "query": "grafana-pyroscope-datasource", "refresh": 1, "current": {"text": "Pyroscope", "value": "pyroscope"}},
    {"name": "ds_prom", "type": "datasource", "query": "prometheus", "refresh": 1, "current": {"text": "Prometheus", "value": "prom"}}
  ]},
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1, "type": "text", "title": "",
      "gridPos": {"h": 6, "w": 16, "x": 0, "y": 0},
      "options": {"mode": "markdown", "content": "### Profiles Drilldown (GA 12.0 · Assistant 12.4)\n\n- **[➡ Open Profiles Drilldown](/a/grafana-pyroscope-app)** — group by service / endpoint / label, compare flame graphs over time.\n- The 12.4 Profiles Assistant surfaces hot paths automatically.\n- Feature toggle: `profilesDrilldown` ✓.\n\n### Sample query\n\nPyroscope is profiling itself (`pyroscope.self`) — the flame graph below queries its own CPU samples."}
    },
    {
      "id": 2, "type": "stat", "title": "Pyroscope backend",
      "gridPos": {"h": 6, "w": 8, "x": 16, "y": 0},
      "datasource": {"uid": "${ds_prom}", "type": "prometheus"},
      "targets": [{"refId": "A", "expr": "up{job=\"pyroscope\"}"}],
      "options": {"reduceOptions": {"calcs": ["lastNotNull"]}, "colorMode": "background"},
      "fieldConfig": {"defaults": {"mappings": [{"type": "value", "options": {"0": {"text": "DOWN", "color": "red"}, "1": {"text": "UP", "color": "green"}}}], "color": {"mode": "thresholds"}, "thresholds": {"mode": "absolute", "steps": [{"color": "red", "value": null}, {"color": "green", "value": 1}]}}, "overrides": []}
    },
    {
      "id": 3, "type": "flamegraph", "title": "Pyroscope self CPU profile",
      "gridPos": {"h": 18, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 6},
      "datasource": {"uid": "${ds_pyro}", "type": "grafana-pyroscope-datasource"},
      "targets": [{"refId": "A", "profileTypeId": "process_cpu:cpu:nanoseconds:cpu:nanoseconds", "labelSelector": "{service_name=\"pyroscope\"}", "groupBy": []}]
    }
  ]
}
